\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Anthropic had to embed its engineers on-site. For six months. Co-building AI agents for trade accounting and client onboarding. Goldman's CIO admitted they were "surprised" it worked beyond coding \'97 and this is a firm with unlimited engineering budget.\cb1 \
