\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Anthropic went Palantir-style. Forward Deployed Engineers learning tribal knowledge, handling exceptions, mapping the real process. Not the SOP. The actual work. Last year's MIT report said 95% of AI pilots never reach production. Because the pilots seldom go deep. \cb1 \
