\ls1\ilvl0
\fs33\fsmilli16800 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 When Nipun and I caught up recently, there was a lot to unpack, be it market cycles, AI bubble, startup and VC ecosystem trends in India and Southeast Asia, and career pivots.
\fs28  \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs33\fsmilli16800 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Our journeys echo a shared theme (beyond a common past employer where we never overlapped): reinvention and resilience.
\fs28 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs33\fsmilli16800 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Nipun\'92s ride has been a rollercoaster one: consulting and ops at Flipkart and Pine Labs, investing at Sequoia Capital India (now Peak XV), co-founding and scaling Ula to $250M+ revenue with top global backers including Jeff Bezos, shutting it down amid Indonesia's slowdown, and now starting all over again by riding the AI wave.
\fs28 \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs33\fsmilli16800 \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Nipun is back in his second avatar as a founder, building
\fs28  {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/neoflo-ai/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 neoflo.ai}}
\fs33\fsmilli16800 , an AI-powered managed service that disrupts back-office operations in finance, vendor management, and more.
