\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Between those: Experiments, hard calls, new people, broken assumptions, and a few theses that now anchor {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/neoflo-ai/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 neoflo.ai}}\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
