\fs28 \cb3 Dear Ula family, Partners & Friends,\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What a journey this has been! We started Ula with a clear purpose \'97\'a0 empowering the backbone of Indonesia\'92s commerce - the neighborhood warung owners. I remember walking through bustling East Java markets, listening to shop owners share their daily struggles. Those insights paved the way for our mission - to bring technology to these true entrepreneurs without losing the community spirit that makes them thrive.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Inspired, we launched in January 2020. Three months later, the pandemic hit. Our small team went from huddling around a table to running a fully remote operation almost overnight. Would warung owners trust a brand-new digital platform in such uncertain times? The answer lay in what came ahead. \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I am very grateful for our team\'92s extraordinary resilience. When supply chains broke, our ops team found creative ways to deliver essentials. When we couldn\'92t visit in person, field teams trained warung owners over WhatsApp. Engineers and product managers poured their hearts into making Ula work. A mid-2020 town hall, dozens of tiny Zoom windows, reminded me of why we existed: stories of customers who stayed afloat during lockdown using Ula\'92s service. That was our culture in action, delivering in the toughest of times. \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We measured success in impact. Our biggest reward was - how many \'93little guys\'94 could stand taller. Customer delight was, is and will remain the primary objective. \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 None of this would have been possible without so many people \'96\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'95 To our investors and advisors \'97 thank you for backing us when Ula was just an idea on a whiteboard.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'95 To the ecosystem supporters \'97 thank you for championing MSMEs and digital inclusion.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'95 To my fellow co-founders \'97 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alan-c-wong/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 Alan Wong}}, your calm, problem-solving leadership; {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/in/derrysakti/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 Derry Sakti}}, your customer insight; {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rikytenggara/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 Riky Tenggara}}, your boundless energy \'97 I couldn\'92t have asked for better partners.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'95 To the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/uladotapp/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 Ula}} team \'97 you were the beating heart of the company. You lived our values, worked through holidays and answered calls at odd hours to serve our customers.\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'95 And most importantly, to our customers, our warung heroes \'97 thank you for trusting us, for embracing new tools in businesses often run for generations, and for letting us be part of your lives.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Ula\'92s chapter closed in 2024. I do not see it as an ending but more of an evolution. The challenges we set out to tackle \'97 fragmented supply chains, lack of credit access, the digital divide \'97 still need bold, committed people to solve them. New leaders will take this mission forward, and I\'92ll be cheering them on.\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 At a personal level, I am proud of everything our tiny set of driven folks achieved, I am humbled by the experience of creating and then closing. In the last few gruelling years, I learned a thing or two about entrepreneurship, about success, about customer obsession, about failure, and most of all - about effort, through which I will continue to fuel my endeavours forward. \cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Stay tuned for what\'92s coming next!\cb1 \
