\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 At Ula, we believe that the mission is bigger than any of us. We are all about our customers, the small traditional retailers, who are among the most vulnerable segment of the retail value chain. Our approach puts our customers at the heart of what we build. My cofounders and I are incredibly proud of every single colleague at Ula who has made our mission the centre of what we do everyday. \cb1 \
