\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 When we launched in January 2020, little did we know that the world was going to see one of the most difficult years in history. Through 2020, we navigated a small ship in a giant storm - the lockdowns, the on-ground hurdles, the masks and sanitisers, remote team-work and many sleepless nights. A year later, we have emerged battle-hardened and stronger. We are both ready and eager to take on even bigger challenges of 2021 and this fundraise brings us just a little bit closer to realising what we have set out to accomplish.\cb1 \
