\fs28 \cb3 About a year ago, I decided to embark on the journey that would become {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/uladotapp/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 Ula}}. I had spent about 5 months understanding Indonesian market. I walked the crowded markets and talked to hundreds of retailers across multiple cities. I saw similar problems to what I had seen in India. But what I loved the most and what finally swung the needle for me is the warm and welcoming people of Indonesia. I felt like I belonged. And that conviction is a matter of the heart. At that point, all the large numbers faded away and it became a voice from within. \cb1 \
